item.title: 【Requests】[REQ AUD] - Nation - Remaster Of The Universe (Qobuz FLAC)
item.description:
I'd love to complete the discography of this amazing Swedish progressive metal band called Nation. If someone can please upload it, it would be greatly appreciated by me.

https://www.qobuz.com/us-en/album/remaster-of-the-universe-nation/ulot1o62nzp4b

I also want to highly thank Sharemania for giving me the chance to request music again.

Kind regards from the Canary Islands, Spain.
